"Friend2Friend is an ambitious project to establish an open source infrastructure of personal data servers. Intended to securely share all kinds* of personal data, these will be 

Distributed - Hosted anywhere on the Internet 

Available - Online 24/7, to receive/initiate data transactions or to act as an intermediary 

Secure - Each has a private key so it can encrypt requests that it makes to friendly servers. 

Networked - Each has a list of friend's servers and their public keys"

URL = http://www.altruists.org/projects/ge/ff/


